name: Drawings are marked for construction, are the latest revision and are entered on drawing register
All conduit is installed to correct positions, is the correct size, is securely glued, saddled, tied in position and the ends sealed for in slab conduits

All concealed conduit runs have been marked up on draft as installed drawings prior to concrete being poured
Concrete pour has been observed to ensure conduits have not been damaged
Final as installed drawings have been drafted and submitted for approval
